snippet.title: BlockMill is coming soon, sign up now.
snippet.description:
Join our Discord server and get Early access NOW!
https://discord.com/invite/MHAeFEbxMd

Quick, claim your house before someone else does!

http://blockmill.co

Join BlockMill a new free social strategy game played on a single world map. Claim your house, your neighbour's house or even a celebrity's house. Take part in fun challenges, team up with friends and build out your empire. Add custom designs to your buildings and alter the structure to make them stand out on the map.

Achieve legendary BlockMill status and stamp your buildings with our City Hall, then a whole new dimension of creativity and player levels unlock - including player to player building trading!

Visit http://blockmill.co and sign up now.
